			<description><![CDATA[<p>
We&rsquo;re looking for someone who loves turning data into interesting insights. If you&#39;re passionate about problem solving, performing analyses, using data to answer interesting questions --- this could be the perfect role for you.</p>
<p>
The selected candidate will conducting analyses on social conversations using our own social monitoring and analytics solution. The goal is to discover and showcase what we can learn about news, events, business practices, user behaviors and more by analyzing what people are saying online.</p>
<p>
The trends you identify and the outcomes you predict will support a host of content marketing initiatives including PR, community management, sales support and customer marketing.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Additional responsibilities include:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Developing strong working knowledge of Brandwatch social monitoring technology and analytics</li>
<li>
Conducting research to identify topics trending on the web that are&nbsp;worthy of analysis</li>
<li>
Proposing content topics that &nbsp;resonate with marketers&nbsp;and give them insights to put into practice</li>
<li>
Providing rationale behind methodologies and overall findings in easy to understand terms&nbsp;</li>
<li>
Possibly interacting with media, analysts and customers as a subject matter expert on social data analysis in the future</li>
</ul>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Bachelor&rsquo;s degree, preferably in statistics, computer science, linguistics or related area of expertise working with statistical model</li>
<li>
Can translate technical data into easy to&nbsp;understand insights for the average business person</li>
<li>
Highly collaborative with a can-do attitude</li>
<li>
Excellent attention to detail, strong interpersonal and communication skills</li>
<li>
Ability to multi-task on multiple projects at any one time</li>
<li>
Experience in SaaS or social media technology sectors a plus but not required</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Why apply to join Brandwatch?</strong><br />
<br />
Successful candidates will be working with a young, energetic and rapidly growing company in an exciting innovative industry. Brandwatch believes strongly in staff development and is looking to hire people who have the potential and desire to build a career with the company. We offer a host of benefits, a fun work experience and opportunities for growth.<br />
Brandwatch is an Equal Opportunity Employer</p>
]]></description>
